### 2.4 Communication Patterns

|  |  |  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| From | To | Protocol | Pattern | Description |
| Browser modules | Python server | HTTP/REST | Sync (fetch) | API calls for data |
| Module → Module | Event Bus | CustomEvent | Pub/Sub | Cross-module coordination |
| Tour → DOM | Direct | DOM API | Sync | Overlay manipulation |
| Tooltips → DOM | Direct | DOM API | Sync | Tooltip injection/positioning |

