## 4. Database Design

No new database tables required. All features use existing KB data via existing queries.

### 4.1 Existing Tables Used

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Table | Used By | Query Pattern |
| entries | Recommendations | WHERE quality\_score < 40 OR updated\_at < NOW()-90d |
| entry\_tags | Recommendations | LEFT JOIN to find entries with 0 tags |
| relationships | Graph Analysis | GROUP BY source\_id/target\_id for degree calculation |
| search\_log | Analytics empty state | COUNT(\*) for zero-result detection |

### 4.2 New Indexes (Performance)

-- Speed up stale entry detection
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx\_entries\_updated\_at ON entries(updated\_at);

-- Speed up orphan detection (entries without relationships)
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx\_relationships\_source ON relationships(source\_id);
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx\_relationships\_target ON relationships(target\_id);

