}

### 5.3 Design Patterns

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Pattern | Where Used | Rationale |
| Module Pattern | All JS files | ES6 modules for encapsulation, no globals |
| Observer/Pub-Sub | event-bus.js | Decouple modules, avoid direct dependencies |
| Strategy | tour.js positioning | Different positioning strategies per step |
| Factory | empty-states.js | Create different empty state UIs per context |
| Singleton | TooltipManager | Only one tooltip visible at a time |

### 5.4 Error Handling

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Error | Handling | User Impact |
| fetch() network error | Catch, log to console, show retry UI | “Unable to load” message |
| localStorage quota exceeded | Catch, continue without persistence | Tour shows every visit |
| DOM element not found (tour target) | Skip step, advance to next | One fewer tour step |
| JSON parse error (config files) | Use empty defaults | Feature disabled gracefully |
| API returns 500 | Show error in UI, enable retry | “Something went wrong” |

