## 7. Security Design

### 7.1 Authentication

No authentication required — KB Web Viewer is a local development tool accessed only on localhost.

### 7.2 Input Validation

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Input | Validation | Sanitization |
| section param (help API) | Whitelist: graph, sessions, browser, stream, dashboard, tags, quality, analytics | Reject if not in whitelist |
| entry\_id (action APIs) | Must be positive integer | parseInt, reject NaN |
| limit param | Integer 1-50 | Clamp to range |
| Config JSON files | Schema validation on load | Reject malformed, use defaults |

### 7.3 XSS Prevention

|  |  |
| --- | --- |
| Context | Protection |
| Tooltip content | textContent (not innerHTML) for user-facing text |
| Help panel markdown | Sanitize HTML output (strip script tags) |
| Tour step content | textContent for titles, innerHTML only for trusted config |
| Recommendation titles | textContent only |

## 8. Performance & Scalability

### 8.1 Loading Strategy

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Resource | Loading | Rationale |
| ui-tokens.css | Sync (in <head>) | Prevent FOUC |
| event-bus.js | Sync module | Required by all other modules |
| tour.js | Async module | Only needed on first visit |
| tooltips.js | Async module | Can load after DOM ready |
| empty-states.js | Async module | Runs after API responses |
| recommendations.js | Async module | Dashboard/Quality only |
| graph-analysis.js | Async module | Graph page only |
| help-panel.js | Async module | Loaded on demand (? click) |

### 8.2 Performance Targets

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Operation | Target | Measurement |
| Tour overlay render | < 50ms | Performance.now() |
| Tooltip show | < 100ms | Time from hover to visible |
| Empty state render | < 50ms | After API response |
| Graph analysis (500 nodes) | < 2000ms | Performance.now() |
| Help panel slide-in | 300ms (animation) | CSS transition |
| Recommendations fetch | < 500ms | Network + render |
| Total additional page load | < 200ms | Lighthouse audit |

### 8.3 Caching Strategy

|  |  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Cache | What | TTL | Technology |
| Tour config | tour-steps.json | Session | Module-level variable |
| Tooltip config | tooltips.json | Session | Module-level variable |
| Help content | API responses | 5 min | localStorage with timestamp |
| Graph analysis | Insight results | Until graph data changes | localStorage with hash |
| Recommendations | API response | 30 sec | In-memory (stale on action) |

